137
00:09:16,280 --> 00:09:17,480
I was ordered by the clan head

138
00:09:18,080 --> 00:09:19,080
to force you into this

139
00:09:19,680 --> 00:09:20,720
and take the Fusang wood.

140
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:22,640
Go take it now.

141
00:09:25,280 --> 00:09:25,960
Yes.

142
00:09:37,000 --> 00:09:38,000
If you hate me,

143
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:39,400
shoot me.

144
00:09:39,760 --> 00:09:41,560
Otherwise, I'm taking the Fusang wood.

145
00:09:43,220 --> 00:09:46,000
