156
00:10:36,720 --> 00:10:37,480
Ms. Duan,

157
00:10:38,520 --> 00:10:39,280
here.

158
00:10:41,280 --> 00:10:41,920
Wait.

159
00:10:42,240 --> 00:10:43,600
The cripple has the Phoenix Gall.

160
00:10:44,160 --> 00:10:45,280
Phoenix Gall?

161
00:10:49,920 --> 00:10:51,920
However, obtaining the Fusang wood

162
00:10:52,600 --> 00:10:53,480
